OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,FAn Indian saree is not just a fashion
OL,7,Fstatement, but a celebration of
OL,8,Fcultural identity.
OL,10,FWhich is why a group of women in
OL,11,FBerkshire get together once a month to
OL,12,Fwear them.
OL,14,FSaree Speak, based in Reading, gives
OL,15,Fmembers a way to show off their
OL,16,Fcollection and share with others why
OL,17,Ftheir outfits are so special.
OL,19,FIt comes as this year's theme for
OL,20,FSouth Asian Heritage Month is 'free to
OL,21,Fbe me'.
