OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,FMohima Bose, Co-founder "We meet once
OL,7,Fa month and we wear our sarees and we
OL,8,Ftalk about it and we get our daughters
OL,9,Fto get involved as well.
OL,11,F"We organise events as well every
OL,12,Fthree or four months... it's mainly a
OL,13,Fladies event and whoever comes has to
OL,14,Fwear a saree and talk about it.
OL,16,F"We have quizzes on sarees, general
OL,17,Fknowledge games on sarees, and we
OL,18,Fdance and have lots of food."
