OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,FAsked why sarees are so important, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "If you see the history of
OL,8,FIndia, in the olden days, it only used
OL,9,Fto be sarees and as fashion moved on
OL,10,Fthey started making the other things.
OL,12,F"But before it was just a cloth
OL,13,Fwrapped around the body. So that's why
OL,14,Fit's very important because it's going
OL,15,Fright back to our ancestors.
OL,17,F"We have to show the world how
OL,18,Fbeautiful sarees are and how rich our
OL,19,Fculture is and keep the culture going."
