OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,FSarees are made up of six yards of
OL,7,Fcolourful hand-woven fabric, paired
OL,8,Fwith a matching blouse and a petticoat.
OL,10,FThe material is wrapped around the
OL,11,Fwaist, pleated, draped over the
OL,12,Fshoulder and then safety-pinned to
OL,13,Fstay in place.
OL,15,FSarees can be passed down through
OL,16,Fgenerations of families and can
OL,17,Fsometimes increase in re-sale value as
OL,18,Folder sarees can have pure gold and
OL,19,Fsilver weaved into the fabric.
