OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,F"When you get a sari - it doesn't end
OL,7,Fthere, you have to get a proper blouse
OL,8,Fdone and accessories and the way you
OL,9,Fcarry yourself. It's the whole package.
OL,11,F"Nowadays sarees are back in trend,
OL,12,Fmore and more youngsters want to buy
OL,13,Fsarees and want to wear them."
OL,15,FAs time moves on, trends have changed
OL,16,Fand there are modern versions of the
OL,17,Ftraditional saree.
