OL,3,CHow Indian sarees are being celebrated
OL,4,Cby a group of women in Reading
OL,6,FThere are some sarees that are machine-
OL,7,Fmade to be more affordable. They are
OL,8,Falso some which are made to be easier
OL,9,Fto wear, coming pre-pleated and pinned.
OL,11,FAn example of a modern take on a saree
OL,12,Fcan be seen by Indian fashion designer
OL,13,FManish Malhotra, on Kim and Khloe
OL,14,FKardashian at the wedding of
OL,15,Fbillionaire Mukesh Ambani's son.
